PrecisEnactment of REGULATIONS AMENDING CERTAIN REGULATIONS ADMINISTERED AND ENFORCED BY THE CANADIAN FOOD INSPECTION AGENCY which, in respect of all three sets of Regulations identified hereinafter, clearly distinguish between the circumstances leading to the suspension of an establishment's registration and the grounds for its cancellation, and in respect of the Fresh Fruit and Vegetable Regulations, by adding a definition of "operator" which is consistent with other Regulations made under this Act. . 1.
